        (2) When should refresh_fafm fire?
        Do NOT pre-list A/B/C/D/E options that bias the answer. Do NOT propose mechanical
        details (stamp shape, verbatim default, chain semantics) before the primary two
        land. Everything mechanical is downstream of Grok's answers to the two primary Qs.
        ORGANIZATION (post-2026-05-30 reorg): Grok-related docs live in ~/export/
