    - text: |
        Path convention for .fafm: default <cwd>/soul.fafm (matches faf-memory-mcp's
        FAF_SOUL_PATH default + the production soul.fafm in faf-memory repo). Env overrides:
        FAF_SOUL_PATH (path), FAF_SOUL_NAMEPOINT (default @local), FAF_SOUL_PROFILE
        (default knowledge in faf-memory-mcp; spec default is voice). Override via path arg
        also supported. For multi-namepoint setups (FAFA-meets-X pattern), per-namepoint
        files like <namepoint>.fafm are possible but not yet wired in production.
      id: "fafm-path-convention"
      type: "reference"
      priority: "standard"
      tags: ["path", "convention", "production"]
      source: "faf-memory-mcp/faf_memory_mcp/server.py + faf-memory/.mcp.json + spec"
      timestamp: "2026-05-30T17:37:31Z"
      confidence_score: 1.0
      verification_status: "verified"

